ire a firearm in Japan</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ZoGY8Y7</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iVp1E1w.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ZoGY8Y7</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kyushutrail]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/bqgCGQZ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9gTar9P.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/bqgCGQZ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Blood on Republican Hands</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4g1SDeE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/TTCxa1n.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4g1SDeE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheRealSleepIsForChumps]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>And he still has got all of his hair, the bastard</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/AZICFhN</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/AyF5Kq4.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/AZICFhN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[NaV3P]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Hard day...One less brother left.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/5z3W20y</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dnYv0Gt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He kept going back and forth between casual chat and unhinged rants of hatred. Slagged any democrat run state, complained that homeless people could sleep in tents in California instead of being forced out by police, railed against abortion rights. Acidic toward trans people, and paranoidly obsessed with pedophiles.

He said he would murder a pedophile in cold blood without hesitation, even if it was me, or our parents. I told him murdering people would make him somewhat worse than a pedophile and he lost his mind, said I wasn't allowed near his children, I was defending pedophiles, I must be one, etc.

Then went right back to chatting.

When we stopped, I confronted him and demanded an apology. He apologized, hesitantly abd, in my opinion, insincerely. Told him "Someone who would say that to me is not my brother", and he got mad, doubled down, told me to fuck off. Got in a shouting match in front of his 3 year old daughter and both our parents. 

I told him in front of everyone that I don't consider him part of my family anymore.

Feeling pretty jumbled about it all, but I am sick of helping him when he's just a poisonous, unstable asshole. I'm so sick of tolerating him.

Just want to scream into the void with a shitty meme. Thank you for reading, if you still are. All men are my brothers, all women are my sisters, everyone between is my beloved sibling. I hope you all have an amazing day, week, year and life.

Front Page Edit: Thank you all for the concern, the advice, and the support. I want to reply to every comment but there are so many. I love you all, and I want the best for you all.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/5z3W20y</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LordOfTheFattys]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>What it feels like to have the soul ripped out of you</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/zp4PKvd</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OEgHTZF.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/zp4PKvd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Potatoid]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2c4dtIe</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/PX8LHAX.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2c4dtIe</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DrDadJokes]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Teacher for 17 years- Say her name, remember her face.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/uJp5SK0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dwwDeDv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A mother & wife who loved hiking. Died protecting her students.We will not forget. Fly High and rest sweetly.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/uJp5SK0</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[mfrybeasley]]></dc:creator></item></channel></rss>